  "notes": "Captures Shopify Admin GraphQL 2025-01 returning OPERATION_IN_PROGRESS for two consecutive bulkOperationRunMutation calls using two uploaded JSONL variable files. The executable comparison hydrates the captured first mutation operation through bulkOperationCancel, registers a local BULK_MUTATION_VARIABLES target through stagedUploadsCreate and the public staged-upload route, and then proves the local throttle response without localSetups or seeded state."
